name: Ksenia Barsk
description: If you want to be somebody, somebody really special, be yourself) I always try to be in constant personal development, it is very important to me. Besides, I am very curious so I always try to know something new I’m sensual and positive, responsible and creative woman. I’m really energetic and rather natural. I like getting new experience, meeting new interesting people. My best friends say that I’m very reliable, sociable, understanding. I’m faithful, cheerful girl and have a good sense of humor. I know that my real destination and happiness lie in a family hearth and reciprocal care.
